apiKey.help:
The Google Cloud Translation API key. Required to call the real API;
without it the tool falls back to the offline demo provider. Resolved from
the OS keychain by the CLI credential preprocessor, or set inline.

The ModernMT authentication key. Required to call the real ModernMT API;
without it the tool falls back to the offline demo provider. Resolved from
the OS keychain by the CLI credential preprocessor, or set inline.

